                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9990" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1494</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">760 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小客户大市场：双童吸管目标市场定位的传奇蜕变</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Small Customers, Big Market: The Legendary Transformation of The Target Market Positioning of SOTON Straw</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张文明，李然，李纯青，董玉成（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">义乌市双童日用品有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">双童吸管；目标市场定位；小客户原则；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SOTON Straw; Target market positioning; Small customer principle</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025年4月，中美贸易战态势急剧升级，中国对美出口的吸管等基础商品供应链遭受巨大冲击，而双童日用品有限公司却依旧稳如磐石。本案例详细讲述了双童在发展过程中，目标市场定位从外贸大客户主导转向国内小客户的历程。其核心是以“小客户原则”为支点，打出“客户分散化、产品创新化、组织裂变化”组合拳：主动调整客户结构，深耕国内中小客户群体；推出可降解吸管等差异化产品，构建专利技术壁垒；推动组织模式创新，孵化多元创业体形成业务矩阵。此组合拳使双童在中美贸易战中，凭借80%以上国内客户、可降解产品技术溢价及创业体协同，保持营收与利润稳定，为其他中小企业在贸易战背景下的目标市场定位及转型发展提供了思路与借鉴范例。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In April 2025, as the China-US trade war escalated sharply, the supply chain of basic commodities such as straws exported from China to the US suffered a massive impact. However, SOTON Daily Necessities Co., Ltd. still remained stable. This case details the journey of SOTON&#39;s target market positioning shift from being dominated by foreign large customers to domestic small customers during its development. At its core, it takes the &quot;Small Customer Principle&quot; as a pivot to deliver a combination strategy of &quot;customer diversification, product innovation, and organizational fission&quot;: actively restructuring its customer base to deeply cultivate domestic small and medium customer groups; launching differentiated products such as degradable straws to build patent-based technical barriers; and promoting organizational model innovation to incubate diversified entrepreneurial entities and form a business matrix. This combination strategy enabled SOTON to maintain stable revenue and profits in the China-US trade war by virtue of its over 80% domestic customer base, the technical premium of degradable products, and the synergy of entrepreneurial entities, providing ideas and reference cases for other SMEs in target market positioning and transformation under trade war contexts.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销学》、《营销战略》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">目标市场定位；市场细分；长尾理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
